Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming all the way out here,\Nit's no wonder it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are pretty far from Clarines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in a hurry, so we\Ncan only take you partway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for allowing me to travel\Nwith you and even ride with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you have to go\Nall the way to Laxdo for an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Court herbalists have it rough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm still an apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we often study outside, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, when I told\NLord Haruka that you passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,he said, "Congratulations."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But he said it with a sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's funny, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell what he's thinking immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's the usual fort inspection.\NFort Laxdo is under my jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold, so don't wander around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a lot that can be\Ngained from being outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This country we experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.58,0:01:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the people we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the feelings we come to know from them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:06.76,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 5: This Path,\Nthe Crystallization of Premonition"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anyone on watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from the royal guards! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone... Even the prince is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular reports stopped coming,\Nso we came to see what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--You can't sta--\N--Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone inside the fort is sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm his attendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a trial period, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I've handed my reins to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This place has been\Npossessed by a fearsome evil spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,About twenty days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One after another, everyone started to\Ncomplain about their bodies feeling strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Like their bodies felt heavy,\Nor their vision was going dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people seemed to\Nlose their sense of balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The physician also fell sick\Nwhile he was tending to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't find the reason behind it,\Nso it must be the work of an evil spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not that sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I was in no state\Nto go down the snowy road...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, wait! What if something\Nhappens to you, as well, Your Highness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, then there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't push myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well to endure it until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, you must come out before sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Mitsuhide, stay outside and keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to avoid having everyone inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, wouldn't the\Nmaster be waiting outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's some kind of sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If we know where that sickness is coming from,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be better than going\Nback empty-handed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right not to stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's worried about the soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide, aren't you\Na close aide of the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Zen's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it really was an evil spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If something like that really exists,\NI'd like to try fighting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the armory, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like it'd have\Nanything to do with... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The armory was empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems the soldier earlier didn't know, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There were claw marks, too. Someone\Nprobably took advantage of this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we switch to bandit hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my specialty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,--Put those away. We need to investigate\Nthe cause and help the soldiers recover first.\N--Specialty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we ask Shirayuki to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She might know something about\Nwhat's happened to the soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he can bring her before sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss Kiki, don't tell me Mitsuhide\Ndoesn't tell Prince Zen his opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell him what's important calmly, Miss Kiki,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't you think your\Npartner's a little soft on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the physician prescribe the medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But there weren't enough\Nmedicinal herbs during this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In cold climates, the medicinal\Nproperties of the herbs are lower,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so a larger amount is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Did you notice anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was often outside keeping watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm not much help...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, i-it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Shuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me know if there's anything I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a great help.\NBut please rest for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like he's weakened considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, you need to go outside soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be bad if you pass out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, that'd be bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I can leave by\Nmyself after calling you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was anything we could do\Ntogether, then I would do it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the case now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to do what I can to be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... stay, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you'd only stay until sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you have to\Nthink of your own position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was being selfish. I take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me if anything happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, good job keeping\Nyour stubbornness in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 'cause of what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're concerned about Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't those feelings show that that's\Nhow much you can depend on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:09:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, it was my first time\Nhearing that you don't like the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay lying down in a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop nagging! I'm cooling my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--Master's actually listening to him.\N--Hey, stop it--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,--Master's actually listening to him.\N--Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, Mitsuhide's\Nreally the only one Zen listens to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that's{\i0} why he doesn't\Nsay usually say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that he's being soft on him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, did you figure anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay being up and about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I rested for a while already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I haven't figured anything out yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone had the same\Nsymptoms at the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's a difference in their symptoms now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason for that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:10:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... But I did figure out\Nwhat medicine the physician was using.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd prepare some with\Nthe medicines I bought in town--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't... start this soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it different depending on the person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuka, you said you were\Noften outside keeping watch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That means, the reason\Nmust be inside the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The people furthest from the\Nentrance have the worst symptoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty cold, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki?! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I was just\Nworking too close to these.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause was the firewood in the fireplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't burn this wood.\NHarmful particles will scatter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you keep breathing them in,\Nthey'll start to have an effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Shuka, a band of travelers said\Nthey didn't want to carry it while they traveled,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so they gave it to them for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for one thing after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you able to move around more easily now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I received medicine from Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to do what I can to be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you stay here for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to leave the soldiers to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To have everyone recovered\Nthis much in just a few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki's skill is undeniable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, apparently there's a band\Nthat uses the Laxdo area as their base.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's their hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a little more time to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have more intel about the town than you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, Mitsuhide. I want to\Ntake care of this with just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we can't just keep relying on Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an infusion of medicinal herbs.\NDo you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't like bitter things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a lot of nutrients, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Shirayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Prince Zen\Nis embarrassed by this fort...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid he'll keep\Nhis distance from us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Zen come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He goes out with the patrols,\Ntalks to the older soldiers about the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and even listens to apprentices\Nlike me like he's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I want to be of use to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He might not come here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he keeps coming here for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Zen having fun here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I need to write the report...\Nand prepare... medicine for the afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, were you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers have starting getting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel all right even when moving around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, take my pulse later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want her to tend to you, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to make a\Ncomplete recovery, then get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer.\NI'm leaving everyone to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, before I prepare the food...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm getting enough sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The master said not to go\Nnear her without permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Prince Zen's attendant right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not wary of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I be after you saved me?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, you're not feeling well, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that, I have\Nto obligation to do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not going to bring up the fact\Nthat I threatened her with an arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, but tell me why you're hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bring hot water! Hot water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's feeling better, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I just want it to end uneventfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What would I follow her for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to note in the south?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably go to the\Nwest tower to check things out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, we're gathering\Nthose who can move to go on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks to Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot cause more trouble than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fulfill our duties\Nwith everything we have, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Don't over do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, Shuka, is there any medicine left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Shirayuki made it in time\Nfor when people woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did everyone take that medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have three shifts right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers wake up every eight hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when does Shirayuki sleep...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes for a slow sixty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you taking my pulse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it. Don't open\Nyour eyes before time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so pale...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who woulda thought the\Nfirewood would work this well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If we just wait for the right\Nchance to sell the weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll make a ton of cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who attacked the fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:19:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're soldiers from the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't do for you to take other\Npeople's things without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourselves soldiers\Nwith such a tiny group?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought us a nice present!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow you to insult anyone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you playing at being friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing that cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can love this country because\NI know those who live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Mitsuhide and Kiki are by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can look forward without\Nforgetting my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there is someone I want to face,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can decide not to become\Nsomeone she would turn her back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NI'm not talking to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,These are words of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too busy listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, Kiki. I'm moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky. I wish he'd say that about me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I wake you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry it took so long for me\Nto notice you weren't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As the person in charge,\NI wasn't paying enough attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, if you had just said something,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have tried to come up with\Na way for you to not be overworked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem you need\Nto deal with by yourself, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it were, don't hide it again. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry, Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're lying here like this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't change the fact that we were\Nall saved thanks to your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't thank you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you were here, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For the soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, you were my driving force...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, that's what you are, Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I met you, over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to\Noperate as usual from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, I'll write you letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I'll look forward to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a lot that can be\Ngained from being outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This country we experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky encounters with the people we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And the feelings we come to know from them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They give us so many lights that never fade...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Prince Izana.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I would welcome Shirayuki, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.99,0:24:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's become a good-for-nothing prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:20.12,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 6: The Back Full of Meaning"
